#: /home/hu-hub/个人项目/开源项目/MouseTiler/src/contents/ui/config_strings.cpp:55
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Will auto tile new windows on the desktop with "
"specified id even if &quot;Auto tile newly opened windows&quot; is not "
"enabled.</p><p>Click Ctrl+Alt+A to toggle auto tiling for current window and "
"print id to logs. Check logs by running this command in a terminal/konsole:</"
"p><p>journalctl -f | grep MouseTiler</p><p>Copy the ids here. Add multiple "
"ids by separating them by a comma.</p><p>Each screen + virtual desktop + "
"activity have their own unique id (screen name + desktop id + activity id "
"smashed together into a long string).</p><p><span style=\" font-"
"weight:700;\">Example </span>(2 ids, one on screen HDMI-A-1 and one on DP-1):"
"</p><p>HDMI-A-11a35dac2-5432-4011-c65f-e36d11c00345f436e08c-"
"e9df-438e-3d74-401cb56dd6bb,DP-16c35dac2-7955-4053-a66b-e36d11c00345f436e08c-"
"e9df-438e-3d74-401cb56dd6bb</p></body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Will auto tile new windows on the desktop with "
"specified id even if &quot;Auto tile newly opened windows&quot; is not "
"enabled.</p><p>Click Ctrl+Alt+A to toggle auto tiling for current window and "
"print id to logs. Check logs by running this command in a terminal/konsole:</"
"p><p>journalctl -f | grep MouseTiler</p><p>Copy the ids here. Add multiple "
"ids by separating them by a comma.</p><p>Each screen + virtual desktop + "
"activity have their own unique id (screen name + desktop id + activity id "
"smashed together into a long string).</p><p><span style=\" font-"
"weight:700;\">Example </span>(2 ids, one on screen HDMI-A-1 and one on DP-1):"
"</p><p>HDMI-A-11a35dac2-5432-4011-c65f-e36d11c00345f436e08c-"
"e9df-438e-3d74-401cb56dd6bb,DP-16c35dac2-7955-4053-a66b-e36d11c00345f436e08c-"
"e9df-438e-3d74-401cb56dd6bb</p></body></html>"

